and they've changed
the direction."

1536
01:28:47,789 --> 01:28:49,586
They didn't change nothing.

1537
01:28:49,657 --> 01:28:53,821
Hormel changed because it was
to their advantage to change.

1538
01:28:53,895 --> 01:28:56,090
They realized
there was profits and growth

1539
01:28:56,164 --> 01:28:57,893
by pursuing this strategy.

1540
