so paternalistic.

1543
01:29:03,004 --> 01:29:06,633
They become barracudas,
just like everybody else.

1544
01:29:09,644 --> 01:29:12,807
We can't look to unions and say,
"You gotta stop this."

1545
01:29:12,880 --> 01:29:16,338
It's gonna take a combination
of outrage from people.

1546
